subtitle: rāingān wičhai chabap sombūn
series: Chut khrōngkān phūmpanyā phatthanākān læ khwāmsamphan rawāng kan khō̜ng rư̄an phư̄nthin Thai-Thai, khunnalaksana khō̜ng sathāpattayakam singwǣtlō̜m nai rư̄an phư̄nthin
title: Khrōngkān phūmpanyā phatthanākān læ khwāmsamphan rawāng kan khō̜ng rư̄an phư̄nthin Thai Khœ̄n Chīang Mai-Chīang Tung
by_statement: ʻŌ̜nsiri Pānin ... [et al.] ; sanapsanun dōi Samnakngān Kō̜ngthun Sanapsanun Kānwičhai (thun songsœ̄m klum wičhai Mēthī Wičhai ʻĀwusō) ; rāingān kānwičhai nī dairap thun sanapsanun kānčhatphim phœ̄iphrǣ phonngān wičhai čhāk Sathāban Wičhai læ Phatthanā, Mahāwitthayālai Sinlapākō̜n.

description.value: Development of local wisdom and relationship between the vernarcular houses of Thai Kern in Chiang Mai, Thailand and Chiang Tung, Myanmar.
